OL,3,C'The pain feels like barbed wire': New
OL,4,Cendometriosis pathway to improve care
OL,6,FA new NHS North West pathway is aiming
OL,7,Fto improve treatment and reduce
OL,8,Fwaiting times for people with
OL,9,Fendometriosis.
OL,11,FThe pathway - launched in Cheshire and
OL,12,FMerseyside - brings together primary
OL,13,Fcare, secondary care and public health
OL,14,Fto reduce waiting times and recognise
OL,15,Fthe condition earlier.
OL,17,FEndometriosis affects one in 10 women
OL,18,Faged 15 to 45, and currently takes an
OL,19,Faverage of eight years to diagnose.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
