OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775537898
OL,3,C'The pain feels like barbed wire': New
OL,4,Cendometriosis pathway to improve care
OL,6,FThe programme, which launched in
OL,7,FJanuary 2026, will include new
OL,8,Flearning resources for healthcare
OL,9,Fprofessionals and a renewed focus on
OL,10,Fraising public awareness of the
OL,11,Fcondition.
OL,13,FCharlotte Martindale, 30, has had
OL,14,Fdebilitating pain, heavy bleeding,
OL,15,Fnausea, bowel issues and fatigue for
OL,16,Fyears but her symptoms were attributed
OL,17,Fto anxiety and depression.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
