PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775537898
OL,3,C'The pain feels like barbed wire': New
OL,4,Cendometriosis pathway to improve care
OL,6,FShe said: "When I got to university
OL,7,Fthe pain became unmanageable. I really
OL,8,Ffelt as if I wasn't being listened to
OL,9,Fand was made to feel like it was all
OL,10,Fin my head."
OL,12,FCharlotte was incorrectly diagnosed
OL,13,Fwith polycystic ovary syndrome (PCOS)
OL,14,Fbefore eventually being referred to
OL,15,Fgynaecology.
OL,17,FShe says she was told a laparoscopy -
OL,18,Fthe only definitive diagnostic
OL,19,Fprocedure - would not be offered
OL,20,Fbecause she was not trying to conceive.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
