CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775537898
OL,3,C'The pain feels like barbed wire': New
OL,4,Cendometriosis pathway to improve care
OL,6,FAfter 14 years of symptoms, an
OL,7,Finternal ultrasound finally revealed
OL,8,Fmultiple endometriomas.
OL,10,FShe was referred to the endometriosis
OL,11,Fcentre in Preston and underwent
OL,12,Fsurgery in 2025, where deep
OL,13,Finfiltrating endometriosis was found
OL,14,Fon her bladder, bowel, and appendix,
OL,15,Fand had stuck her ovaries to her
OL,16,Fpelvic wall.
OL,18,FAlthough the surgery was successful,
OL,19,FCharlotte has been told its likely
OL,20,Ffurther surgery will be needed as the
OL,21,Fendometriosis regrows.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
