CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775537898
OL,3,C'The pain feels like barbed wire': New
OL,4,Cendometriosis pathway to improve care
OL,6,FData from the NHS Confederation showed
OL,7,Fthat 84% of women reported being
OL,8,Fdismissed by medical professionals.
OL,10,FMillie Campbell, 20, is still waiting
OL,11,Ffor a formal diagnosis.
OL,13,FShe has had heavy, erratic bleeding,
OL,14,Fpain and severe bloating since she was
OL,15,F12, but she was told she was "too
OL,16,Fyoung" to have endometriosis.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
