PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775537898
OL,3,C'The pain feels like barbed wire': New
OL,4,Cendometriosis pathway to improve care
OL,6,F"I've been on several different
OL,7,Fcontraceptive pills, but none of them
OL,8,Fhave worked," she said. "The pain
OL,9,Ffeels like a ball of barbed wire, and
OL,10,Fregular pain relief just doesn't touch
OL,11,Fit".
OL,13,FAfter an MRI last year, she is still
OL,14,Fwaiting to find out whether she will
OL,15,Fbe offered a laparoscopy.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@MO]pD@YOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
