PN,39507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775537898
OL,3,C'The pain feels like barbed wire': New
OL,4,Cendometriosis pathway to improve care
OL,6,FDr Paula Cowan, NHS England North
OL,7,FWest's Medical Director for Primary
OL,8,FCare and National Specialty Advisor
OL,9,Fwith the Women's Team, says the new
OL,10,Fapproach marks an important step
OL,11,Fforward, but warns that significant
OL,12,Fchallenges remain.
OL,14,FShe said: "Early consideration and
OL,15,Frecognition of endometriosis is key,
OL,16,Fboth in general practice and in the
OL,17,Fcommunity. The earlier endometriosis
OL,18,Fis recognised and diagnosed, the
OL,19,Fbetter the care the NHS can give.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
