PN,39508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1775537898
OL,3,C'The pain feels like barbed wire': New
OL,4,Cendometriosis pathway to improve care
OL,6,F"In this new pathway, we've looked
OL,7,Fclosely at how engaging with patients
OL,8,Fand GPs, workforce planning and better
OL,9,Fuse of data can help reduce waiting
OL,10,Flists and ensure people get the help
OL,11,Fthey need.
OL,13,F"Too many women feel that they have
OL,14,Fnot been listened to regarding their
OL,15,Fheavy, painful periods are normal.
OL,17,F"From the very first contact with a
OL,18,Fpatient presenting with heavy painful
OL,19,Fperiods, we need to be thinking could
OL,20,Fthis be endometriosis."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
