OL,3,C'The pain feels like barbed wire': New
OL,4,Cendometriosis pathway to improve care
OL,6,FDr Cowan says the new pathway is part
OL,7,Fof a wider commitment to improving
OL,8,Fwomen's health across the region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
